WEBVTT

00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:01.968
Boa notícia:

00:00:01.968 --> 00:00:04.873
não precisa de terminal para este!

00:00:04.873 --> 00:00:07.777
Vamos abrir um VS Code completo

00:00:07.777 --> 00:00:09.229
direto no navegador,

00:00:09.229 --> 00:00:10.682
criar alguns arquivos,

00:00:10.682 --> 00:00:13.586
rodar alguns comandos e ver o

00:00:13.586 --> 00:00:16.491
kernel manter tudo dentro do repo.

00:00:17.241 --> 00:00:19.448
A ideia é a seguinte.

00:00:19.448 --> 00:00:22.096
O editor não roda no seu

00:00:22.096 --> 00:00:22.537
computador.

00:00:22.537 --> 00:00:25.185
Ele roda dentro do sandbox do

00:00:25.185 --> 00:00:26.509
repo no servidor,

00:00:26.509 --> 00:00:29.157
e o seu navegador acessa através

00:00:29.157 --> 00:00:30.922
de um túnel SSH.

00:00:30.922 --> 00:00:33.129
Então a árvore de arquivos,

00:00:33.129 --> 00:00:35.777
o terminal integrado e tudo que

00:00:35.777 --> 00:00:38.425
você iniciar a partir dele veem

00:00:38.425 --> 00:00:41.073
exatamente o que o repo vê,

00:00:41.073 --> 00:00:42.397
e nada mais.

00:00:45.665 --> 00:00:46.398
One command.

00:00:46.398 --> 00:00:48.963
The CLI installs the editor server on

00:00:48.963 --> 00:00:50.063
the machine once,

00:00:50.063 --> 00:00:52.261
starts it inside the repo sandbox,

00:00:52.261 --> 00:00:53.361
opens a tunnel,

00:00:53.361 --> 00:00:55.193
and hands you a link.

00:00:55.193 --> 00:00:56.659
No local VS Code,

00:00:56.659 --> 00:00:58.491
no extensions to set up.

00:01:01.491 --> 00:01:04.211
Esse URL é o seu editor.

00:01:04.211 --> 00:01:06.477
Funciona em qualquer sistema operacional,

00:01:06.477 --> 00:01:09.197
o único requisito é um navegador.

00:01:09.707 --> 00:01:10.495
E pronto:

00:01:10.495 --> 00:01:11.284
VS Code,

00:01:11.284 --> 00:01:13.255
em uma aba do navegador.

00:01:13.255 --> 00:01:16.014
A árvore de arquivos à esquerda mostra

00:01:16.014 --> 00:01:16.803
o repo,

00:01:16.803 --> 00:01:18.380
e apenas o repo.

00:01:22.207 --> 00:01:24.530
Vamos criar um arquivo de verdade,

00:01:24.530 --> 00:01:26.079
sem usar o terminal.

00:01:26.079 --> 00:01:27.241
Um novo editor,

00:01:27.241 --> 00:01:29.952
algumas linhas e salvar como notes barra

00:01:29.952 --> 00:01:31.113
todo ponto md.

00:01:31.113 --> 00:01:33.824
A pasta aparece à esquerda quando o

00:01:33.824 --> 00:01:35.373
arquivo chega ao repo.

00:01:40.707 --> 00:01:42.997
O terminal integrado também funciona,

00:01:42.997 --> 00:01:45.746
e lá está o nosso arquivo.

00:01:45.746 --> 00:01:48.494
Agora vamos tentar olhar fora do

00:01:48.494 --> 00:01:48.952
repo:

00:01:48.952 --> 00:01:49.868
permissão negada.

00:01:49.868 --> 00:01:52.159
Isso não é uma configuração,

00:01:52.159 --> 00:01:53.533
é o kernel.

00:01:59.707 --> 00:02:01.718
Same repo from the plain terminal:

00:02:01.718 --> 00:02:03.730
the working directory is the repo,

00:02:03.730 --> 00:02:05.741
the files are the repo's files.

00:02:08.623 --> 00:02:10.439
Terminal e editor confirmam,

00:02:10.439 --> 00:02:12.254
é o mesmo sandbox.

00:02:15.535 --> 00:02:18.165
And the file we created in the

00:02:18.165 --> 00:02:18.916
browser editor?

00:02:18.916 --> 00:02:19.667
Right here.

00:02:19.667 --> 00:02:22.297
Files made in VS Code are real

00:02:22.297 --> 00:02:23.048
repo files,

00:02:23.048 --> 00:02:23.424
instantly.

00:02:25.174 --> 00:02:27.102
Criado no navegador,

00:02:27.102 --> 00:02:29.030
legível pelo terminal.

00:02:29.030 --> 00:02:30.315
Um repo,

00:02:30.315 --> 00:02:31.600
duas portas.

00:02:34.916 --> 00:02:36.387
Now try to leave.

00:02:36.387 --> 00:02:38.593
Listing the root of the server:

00:02:38.593 --> 00:02:39.329
permission denied.

00:02:39.329 --> 00:02:41.167
The kernel scopes the editor,

00:02:41.167 --> 00:02:41.903
its terminal,

00:02:41.903 --> 00:02:44.477
and every child process to this repo.

00:02:46.227 --> 00:02:48.526
Negado pelo kernel,

00:02:48.526 --> 00:02:50.824
não pela configuração.

00:02:54.130 --> 00:02:55.701
Other users' homes?

00:02:55.701 --> 00:02:56.748
Also denied.

00:02:56.748 --> 00:02:59.367
Whatever runs inside this sandbox

00:02:59.367 --> 00:03:00.414
— editors,

00:03:00.414 --> 00:03:00.938
terminals,

00:03:00.938 --> 00:03:03.556
build tools — ends at

00:03:03.556 --> 00:03:05.128
the repo's walls.

00:03:06.878 --> 00:03:08.808
O sandbox não tem exceções.

00:03:08.808 --> 00:03:10.352
Esse é o ponto.

00:03:11.162 --> 00:03:11.660
Navegador,

00:03:11.660 --> 00:03:12.159
editor,

00:03:12.159 --> 00:03:12.657
terminal:

00:03:12.657 --> 00:03:13.654
mesmo sandbox,

00:03:13.654 --> 00:03:14.651
mesmas regras.

00:03:14.651 --> 00:03:17.643
A seguir vem o recurso em

00:03:17.643 --> 00:03:20.135
que tudo aqui se baseia,

00:03:20.135 --> 00:03:21.132
o fork.

00:03:21.132 --> 00:03:23.126
Você vai gostar deste.
